<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="B">B</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_science_fiction_authors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: B">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:172px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Gravure-cyrano2.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/27/Gravure-cyrano2.jpg/170px-Gravure-cyrano2.jpg" width="170" height="237" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/27/Gravure-cyrano2.jpg/255px-Gravure-cyrano2.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/27/Gravure-cyrano2.jpg/340px-Gravure-cyrano2.jpg 2x" data-file-width="896" data-file-height="1251" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Gravure-cyrano2.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.23wmf21/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
<b>Cyrano de Bergerac</b>, one of the earliest SF writers</div>
</div>
