<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="V">V</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_science_fiction_authors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: V">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright">
